set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+2]= "There is a castle over the northern mountains, it's abandoned... "
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+3]= "Did you know about some maidens lost?, they dissapeared in the middle of the night"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+4]= "Did you entered into the castle over the hills?, rumors say there appears a Vampire at midnight..."
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+5]= "I'm afraid of my kids. Some incursioners are kidnapping childs..."
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+6]= "Why the bears come here? they are very angry..."
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+7]= "Have you seen Misha, the King of bears... People runs horrified when a rumor says He is over us..."
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+8]= "Did you know about a secret entrance into the graveyard.. That's the thieves base"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+9]= "There's a Pirates cave beyond the graveyard but I don't know how to reach here?'"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+10]= "Yesterday I went to the beach, I saw some undeads wandering... Soldiers are killing them    ...again "
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+11]= "Nobody can walk free here!!!, If not are the beasts, there are bandits collecting taxes!!... the government is doing wrong things "
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+12]= "God, there are undeads in the church catacombs! why they started to appear??"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+13]= "Yesterday I was in mass, I swear I saw a zombie back the parson"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+14]= "Few days ago, We had to leave the liturgy when zombies started to walk from the catacombs... into the mass!, It was disturbing"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+15]= "Reinhard is requesting asistance to rescue lost scouts, they are checking some pirate base"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+16]= "Velhimen was good place to live until the government allowed bandits to work for him"
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+17]= "The pirates have arrived to the coast, I'm afraid that they can assault us..."
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+18]= "What is happening in Enthashara? there is something rare in the air..."
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+19]= "I hope those bears will return some day to their natural home..."
set s__dialg[(1)*(22)+20]= "The kobols became crazy, they are attacking our childs!"
call TriggerSleepAction(0.1)

set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+0]= "Did you know why the government has closed the culvert?"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+1]= "The brotherhood of Wolf's Fang has a permanently speaker in the kingdom, We mustn't abandon Enthashara..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+2]= "There's an abandoned farm on the northern fields. People says the owner was a strange guy."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+3]= "The main entrance to the culver was clausured. What is happening on the sewers?"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+4]= "There's an enchanted monastery to the sourthern way, I'm scary about his guard"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+5]= "Those ogres have kidnapped some of us... "
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+6]= "Did you know there is a huge cavern that connects this place with winter lands, the entrance is kept by trolls "
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+7]= "Have you visited the ruined altar on the north?, I've stayed over there. it feels magical!"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+8]= "Take care of walk in the outlaw suburb... There are bandits living in that place"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+9]= "I don't know when monsters started to appear down us. But it seems they come from a secret entrance..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+10]= "Long time ago there was a huge sanctuary south of the suburbs. But the war against Iveor devastated that place completely"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+11]= "Beyond the suburbs there is a Castle owned by a succubus. I don't know where she come from..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+12]= "The way to Ekrom city is very dangerous. You must travel across the Spiders forest to reach the desert lands..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+13]= "Why our gateways are owned by bandits? I don't know who gives them their authority..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+14]= "People says there a secret entrance to the culvert, from the suburbs..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+15]= "I'm scared, I've heard there is a Werewolf wandering in our lands..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+16]= "We are waiting for suplies from Colddream, I don't how many more days we can resist"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+17]= "Have you seen a maiden wandering on the fields?... she went crazy some weeks ago..."
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+18]= "I hope some day we will see the return of Valkan...to his throne"
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+19]= "Some guy told me that he saw the farm's owner doing strange rituals on his house... "
set s__dialg[(2)*(22)+20]= "I think Wolf'sfang brotherhood is corrupt, They want political power..."

call TriggerSleepAction(0.1)
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+0]= "I've heard the alchemist is collecting some ancients scroll. He is tryng to decrypt some secrets!"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+1]= "Our troops have been sent to the southern to stop the undeads, now you can see any kind of people wandering in our cities,"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+2]= "Those orcs... they are being rising from the caves in the northern mountains"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+3]= "I've heard there is a huge fortress being constructed into the caves, I'm afraid the orcs some day will fall over us..."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+4]= "I don't know where, but there is a scorpions nest on the desert, The mighty scorpion king lives here"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+5]= "Are you visiting the Ekrom library? there are some books that I can't understand..."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+6]= "Ekrom is recruiting supporters to handle the Orcs advance, I would like to fight but I'm too weak..."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+7]= "Have you walked at night here?... There come some smugglers to the city, I don´t like that people."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+8]= "Henry has allowed the help of the bandits sindycate, Enthashara's ways become very dangerous these days."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+9]= "People says there's a Werewolf wandering in Valdivia... How's that possible?"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+10]= "I'm afraid that the news says there is a huge undead army coming from the south."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+11]= "Our main force is left... that's the reason why the bandits have taken the waygates control..."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+12]= "Enthashara is falling into the darkness... Our faith has decayed long time ago."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+13]= "This city is legendary. My grandpa told me some stories about a great king wizzard named Avahor and the ancient war of Amanecer"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+14]= "Ekrom is the capital of Enthashara. This place was the main bastion against Iveor in the ancient war"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+15]= "It's rare. there are some battles bettween Orc tribes. It seems to be an orc war but who is the good guy?"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+16]= "Yesterday I listened the Pvp master talking with a new peon. He told him something like <Exiled of Kendor>."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+17]= "The zephyr ride has published a new destiny for traveling: Colddream... I've heard that's a Winter place."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+18]= "The <Army of Ekrom> will protect us, they are the real heir to the Throne.."
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+19]= "I don't understand these orcs. Some of them seem to be friendly but there are others that hate us!"
set s__dialg[(3)*(22)+20]= "I remember when I was kid the brigde to Valdivia was working. I hope some day it be rebuilded..."

call TriggerSleepAction(0.1)
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+0]= "The dams have been invaded by monsters, I'm afraid of drink our water..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+1]= "Colddream is home of the Ancient Core brotherhood. They are Magic followers."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+2]= "I don't like that guy Huggs. He always is crying for money but he is rich!"
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+3]= "The way to Ekrom is blocked by undeads! I don't know where they came..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+4]= "Have you traveled to the winter forest? You must take care of wolfs, they always are angry."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+5]= "Captain Daryun is leading Colddream's defense against the undead siege. he'll protect us..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+6]= "There is a small village across the mountains named Varanger. You can reach that place easily using zephyrs!"
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+7]= "Have you talked with Claire?, she always stay on the tarvern..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+8]= "There's is a misteryous entrance to the mountain across the winter forest. It was a sanctuary"
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+9]= "If you walk across the winter forest you will reach some great falls... there's a huge cave entrace following back the river"
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+10]= "Strange things started when the undeads blocked the way, Monsters, monsters every where... "
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+11]= "The undead siege has blocked three main ways. EKrom, Valdivia and Dhor..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+12]= "I believe those undeads have come from Dhor. The house of Santino is located on the summits of Dhor"
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+13]= "I've seen Ekrom forces traveling via Zephyr to Varanger. I believe they found something wrong there..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+14]= "Rumors say that an unknown menace comes from the east. I'm afraid... maybe the end is near..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+15]= "Yesterday someone starts talking about the cult of Irntu-hell on the tavern. What is that cult?"
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+16]= "I remember some old stories of Ancient Core, they were followers of Ghost magic..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+17]= "People says the real menace comes from the East... Lots of troops have been sent to Varanger."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+18]= "Colddream was a beautifull port. Many merchant ships, mostly from the south docked every day on our shores"
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+19]= "I like the sound of the shores, the sea, the wind, the sleeping ships, love the port life..."
set s__dialg[(4)*(22)+20]= "When the undeads come we were forced to destroy our main bridge... I liked a lot that bridge.."

call TriggerSleepAction(0.1)
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+0]= "Our village was kinda outpost location for foreigners.."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+1]= "The land of Serantas starts beyond the eastern mountains. I would like to travel there"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+2]= "Our village always was hidden by the Winter keeper power, but it has changed last years...!"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+3]= "I ve seen some misterious travelers passing across the mountains. They tell us something about a menace from Serantas.."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+4]= "Blackhand brotherhood... yes, They talked something related to that name..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+5]= "There are lots of powerfull warriores in this invernal place. The magnataur lord controls all the high fields..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+6]= "Serantas is a beautifull forest place, I've visited Taneryn when I was child...!"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+7]= "Have you walkedacross the mountains?? I ve seen some military forces keeping that way..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+8]= "Yesterday I heard from the guard something evil related to <Cult of Irntu-Hel>... that name sounds me disturbing"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+9]= "If you walk across the winter forest you will reach some great falls... there's a huge cave entrace following back the river"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+10]= "Bypassing magnataurs location there is a huge cavern, be carefull to enter there... "
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+11]= "This place was hidden from Enthashara, but the protecting powers have been weakened, What is happening?..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+12]= "I believe those undeads have come from Dhor. The house of Santino is located on the summits of Dhor"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+13]= "I've seen Ekrom forces traveling via Zephyr to Varanger. I believe they found something wrong Here..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+14]= "Rumors say that an unknown menace comes from the east. I'm afraid... maybe the end is near..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+15]= "Yesterday someone starts talking about the cult of Irntu-hell on the tavern. What is that cult?"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+16]= "I remember my grandpa talking about a huge graveyard beyond the mountains, that place was a battlefield long time ago..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+17]= "People says the real menace comes from the East... I dont know what are talking they about."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+18]= "Welcome to Varanger, the last stand before Serantas land"
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+19]= "To reach Taneryn you must take the east passage to the mountain..."
set s__dialg[(5)*(22)+20]= "I've heard a lot of some undead invasion into Enthashara, Hope they will not reach here..."



//============================================
     
endfunction

//===========================================================================
function InitTrig_setherotype takes nothing returns nothing
    set gg_trg_setherotype=CreateTrigger()
    call TriggerRegisterTimerEventSingle(gg_trg_setherotype, 5)
    call TriggerAddAction(gg_trg_setherotype, function Trig_setherotype_Actions)
endfunction


